{"tid":109740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人在日本攪 反APA大遊行 到場僅30人左右 沿途被日本人招呼侮辱","createTime":"2017-02-06T07:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T18:38:49.000Z","uid":54373,"like":230,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c420e7415ff223d10216546c05574d0f21f3327","tid":109740,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:13:55.000Z","msg":"2017-02-05 19:02:58 作者: 良知媒體<br />\n<br />\n今天（2月3日）下午，在日&ldquo;小粉紅&rdquo;舉行反對APA酒店遊行。號稱&ldquo;千人大遊行&rdquo;，到場僅30人左右。據在場人士表示：此次遊行沒有喊口號，原定向APA酒店遞交的抗議書也沒有遞交；相反反對側聲勢浩大，一直在用擴音器演講，人數也遠遠超過&ldquo;小粉紅&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lzmtnews.org/upload/original/65MD314862927441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lzmtnews.org%2Fupload%2Foriginal%2F65MD314862927441.jpg&h=074b42cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下圖為參與遊行的&ldquo;小粉紅&rdquo;合影。可以看出，到場人數不足以舉起所有準備好的條幅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lzmtnews.org/upload/original/65MD314862927442.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lzmtnews.org%2Fupload%2Foriginal%2F65MD314862927442.jpg&h=89c4452e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本出動大量警察維持秩序，分隔開立場對立的人群，保護遊行隊伍。不同立場的到場者均表示，日本警察的專業素質值得稱道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lzmtnews.org/upload/original/65MD314862927443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lzmtnews.org%2Fupload%2Foriginal%2F65MD314862927443.jpg&h=456e45b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反對側不乏在日華人，有人舉著中文標語：&ldquo;你在日本遊行示威，絕不會像在天安門、維吾爾、西藏那樣被鎮壓。放心吧！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n用來諷刺這些在國內沒有遊行自由的&ldquo;小粉紅&rdquo;，來到自由的土地上&ldquo;愛國&rdquo;的荒誕現實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n流亡日本的政治漫畫家變態辣椒也帶著漫畫來到現場。這幅漫畫表現的​​是，一隻代表中國的熊貓，掩蓋起&ldquo;長春圍城&rdquo;、&ldquo;大饑荒&rdquo;、&ldquo;文革&rdquo;、&ldquo;天安門&rdquo;等殘害幾千萬中國人民的慘痛歷史，視而不見，卻單單對否定&ldquo;南京大屠殺&rdquo;的APA酒店暴跳如雷。<br />\n<br />\n變態辣椒在現場還舉著另一個標語，用日文寫著：&ldquo;日本是有言論自由的國家，讓我們把中國也變成有言論自由的國家！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在日維吾爾活動家也參與了遊行，呼籲人們關注中國少數民族的人權狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lzmtnews.org/upload/original/65MD314862927445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lzmtnews.org%2Fupload%2Foriginal%2F65MD314862927445.jpg&h=83014c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lzmtnews.org/upload/original/65MD314862927446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lzmtnews.org%2Fupload%2Foriginal%2F65MD314862927446.jpg&h=0d8e4bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本右翼人士和宣傳車大量來到現場，演講、遊行，人數和氣勢上遠超小粉紅隊伍。他們舉出中文標語：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&ldquo;沒有共產黨，才有新中國&rdquo;[size=5]</span></span>、&ldquo;中國共產黨是亞洲的敗類&rdquo;等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n良知媒體獨家報導。"},{"pid":"060342d0a57bb81ffe1b94402f40f2a48d1399f0","tid":109740,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"反對側不乏在日華人，有人舉著中文標語：&ldquo;你在日本遊行示威，絕不會像在天安門、維吾爾、西藏那樣被鎮壓。放心吧！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢句真係笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39adb54cdcafe095124b3516094a2557b9475061","tid":109740,"uid":14094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"正評不解釋"},{"pid":"aa2521181f978f133967cd68fecf5bcbc24b6e4b","tid":109740,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"：&ldquo;沒有共產黨，才有新中國&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a1910ad6f86bb978fbc38933fa571f2ed496e7c0","tid":109740,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:22:55.000Z","msg":"日本右翼人士和宣傳車大量來到現場，演講、遊行，人數和氣勢上遠超小粉紅隊伍。他們舉出中文標語：&ldquo;沒有共產黨，才有新中國&rdquo;、&ldquo;中國共產黨是亞洲的敗類&rdquo;等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858144a0f936c995d06746af8451161bbeb57774","tid":109740,"uid":14094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反對側不乏在日華人，有人舉著中文標語：&ldquo;你在日本遊行示威，絕不會像在天安門、維吾爾、西藏那樣被鎮壓。放心吧！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢句真係笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能應該加埋香港落去"},{"pid":"807ecf1da21a6d57eb64bfb2ce80b4c09cf11a7d","tid":109740,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"諗起前年嗰次本土派大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0073e641699bb324ee5523cc7c8147c7afff72c","tid":109740,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本右翼人士和宣傳車大量來到現場，演講、遊行，人數和氣勢上遠超小粉紅隊伍。他們舉出中文標語：&ldquo;沒有共產黨，才有新中國&rdquo;、&ldquo;中國共產黨是亞洲的敗類&rdquo;等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本人好天真<br />\n有冇共產黨中國都一樣咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09af4395d99d7fb48f3fad5927c16ab180476b0e","tid":109740,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121be58b1b0f2f1192ec81d8dad48994e0bb11e0","tid":109740,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd9ef5d41f70674f4590841c47afe550261e03a","tid":109740,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:26:19.000Z","m